# 📁 .gitignore für Python, IDEs, temporäre Dateien und mehr

---

## 🐍 Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

---

## 📦 Virtual Environments
.env
.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/

---

## 🛠️ IDEs & Editoren

### **VS Code**
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

### **PyCharm**
.idea/
*.iml

### **Jupyter Notebooks**
.ipynb_checkpoints/

---

## 🗃️ Betriebssysteme

### **macOS**
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.fseventsd
.Spotlight-V100
.TemporaryItems
.Trashes
.VolumeIcon.icns
.com.apple.timemachine.donotpresent

### **Windows**
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
*.tmp
*.temp

### **Linux**
*~
.nfs*

---

## 📝 Logs & Temporäre Dateien
*.log
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.tmp/
temp/

---

## 🔐 Sensible Daten (NIEMALS committen!)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.config.json
secrets.yml
secrets.json
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

---

## 📦 Paketmanager
### **npm**
node_modules/
package-lock.json

### **pip**
Pipfile.lock

---

## 📄 Markdown & Dokumentation
*.md.swp

---

## 🗑️ Sonstiges
.cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/
.nox/
.coverage
*.cover
*.py,cover
.hypothesis/
